        --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        
          - Hotfix release for off-by-one error (#621)
        
        
        0.32 Release                                               2015-05-18
        --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        
          - Hotfix release for MPIRUN_RSH on Stampede (#572).
        
        
